entries.en-US:
```kotlin
// BAD — swallows cancellation
try { fetchData() } catch (e: Exception) { log(e) }

// GOOD — preserves cancellation
try { fetchData() } catch (e: CancellationException) { throw e } catch (e: Exception) { log(e) }
// or use runCatching and check
```

